For QUADRATS, the distance along transect in DECImeters.  For BELTTRANS, the total distance of the SEGMENT (usually each vertical foot) in DECImeters.  Decimeters are to make INTEGER vals.  Weird, yes, but that's the scale at which it was measured, and otherwise it'll be the only decimal num.
